<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/992203-just-finished-this-and-need-a-little-help">Just finished this and need a little help: 1) still not sure why Mr. Bevins appears with multiple eyes, legs, etc and 2) still a bit unclear on the reverend&#39;s journey--am struggling with why he was turned back to the &quot;Bardo&quot; and what he decided to finally do--more faith, more sacrifice? Any help or speculation appreciated!</a>
</div>
